<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><!--
I spent a significant amount of time trying to display one log item per line instead of
wrapping the log item to fit the width of the screen.

Things I tried:

    1) set the TextView.lines to 1, and set a constant width and height.
    2) use a GridLayoutManager

In every case the layout_width and height were overriden by the RecyclerView :(

I finally decided it wasn't worth the time, and added dividers between the items instead.
-->

<TextView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:id="@android:id/text1"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
    android:paddingStart="?android:attr/listPreferredItemPaddingStart"
    android:paddingEnd="?android:attr/listPreferredItemPaddingEnd"
    android:textSize="24sp"
    />

